               <head>Confirmation; Great Waldingfield; 1526</head>
               <msContents>
                  <textLang mainLang="la">Latin</textLang>
                  <msItem>
                     <p> 
                        <pb n="535"/> 
                        <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Holmes</surname>
                        </persName> and others, feoffees, under 
                  the will of <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> 
                           <surname>Parker</surname></persName>, confirm a sale of
                  one croft of land, called <placeName type="minor">Upstretecroft</placeName>, with
                  a toft or garden within the same in <placeName key="place_105311">Great Waldingfield (Great Waldingfeld)</placeName>, which the executors of
                  <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> 
                           <surname>Parker</surname>
                        </persName> had made to
                  <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> 
                           <surname>Crane</surname>, esq.</persName>, and
                  <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Waspe</surname></persName>. 
                  Dated <origDate when="1526-09-06">6 Sept., 18 Hen. VIII (1526)</origDate>.
                     </p>
                  </msItem>
